headline: 3 Important Takeaways From GM's Strong Q1
summary: Tariffs could eat billions from automakers' bottom lines.  General Motors posted a strong first quarter, topping estimates.  All eyes and ears are on automakers' earnings calls to try and pick up any hints or details about how companies will try to mitigate tariffs.
